@node Main "X_Next - Documentation"

                              'X_Next' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'X_Next' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} in which you move to all the tiles
that are shown on the game board. You can move on any tile except
those that are immediately next, either horizontally, vertically or
diagonally, to your position. As you leave a tile, it disappears, if
it has a number on it, that number will decrease by one.

  Have fun!

