1.0: -First public release.

@endnode

@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place 'X_Next' where you want on
your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or Libraries are
needed.

                             How to play?

  The goal is to remove all the tiles that are shown on a game board. You
can move on any tile, by clicking on them, except those that are located
next to your current position (your position is indicated by an 'X' shaped
object).

  As you move from one tile to another, the previous tile you were on will
disappear (unless it has a number on it), just watch out that there are at
least one tile that is not immediately next to your position because
otherwise, the game will be over.

  Some tiles have numbers from 2 to 5 on them; every time you leave such a
tile, its number will decrease by one, so you can go to these tiles that
number of times before they disappear.

  Have fun!

@endnode

